trk.name: E2 Solo
trk.desc: Good workout. Tried to keep it in zone 2 as much as possible, with a gear that allowed 70rpm or so. Occasionally had to go below 60rpm & above 170bpm, but not too much. Cold for last hour or so. Got feet up for half hour after before shower. Bit of discomfort in right side. Forgot about pedaling in circles when climbing, esp in Glencree valley. 1:17 in zone 2.
